  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414990/extras/b848dd581deb9b9da2a44cab3b405960.poster.avif?t=1712983402\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414990/extras/b848dd581deb9b9da2a44cab3b405960.webm?t=1712983402\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414990/extras/b848dd581deb9b9da2a44cab3b405960.mp4?t=1712983402\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You are faced with a difficult task of surviving and overcoming all the difficulties that you will encounter. You stay in your apartment and can’t leave the house. Life continues within four walls. Master a variety of online professions, order groceries, develop skills, grow vegetables, satisfy your needs and plan your budget wisely. The game also has common and epic quests, try to complete them all.",
